---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Programmatic SEO Directory Websites | Stackbase System" description="Programmatic SEO directory websites with scalable templates, clean indexing controls, and practical architecture for sustainable growth.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="text-sm text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-wider">PROGRAMMATIC SEO</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-5 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Programmatic SEO for directory websites (without bloating low-quality pages)</h1>
      <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg max-w-3xl">Most pSEO projects fail because they publish too many weak pages too early. Stackbase builds pSEO directory systems with quality-first templates, controlled indexation, and internal links designed for crawl efficiency.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5"><p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Template Layer</p><p class="text-white text-2xl font-['JetBrains_Mono'] mt-1">3-5 core types</p></div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5"><p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Indexation Rule</p><p class="text-white mt-1">Quality over page count</p></div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5"><p class="text-xs text-[#8b8b9a]">Primary Goal</p><p class="text-white mt-1">Sustainable ranking growth</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">What gets implemented</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]">
          <li>• Page template architecture (city/category/city+category models)</li>
          <li>• Programmatic title/meta patterns with intent-aware variation</li>
          <li>• Canonical + noindex control where duplication risk is high</li>
          <li>• Internal linking modules to support crawl and discovery</li>
          <li>• Sitemap structure aligned with indexing priorities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">How we avoid common pSEO mistakes</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]">
          <li>• No mass-publishing of thin pages just to inflate URL counts</li>
          <li>• No keyword stuffing in templates</li>
          <li>• No blind duplication across geo/attribute combinations</li>
          <li>• No indexation without QA on content quality</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">Who should choose this</h2>
        <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] mb-4">Founders who want scalable SEO with discipline. If your business model depends on long-tail discovery, pSEO can be a strong growth engine — but only if architecture and content controls are handled correctly from the start.</p>
        <a href="/case-studies/indoorclimbinggym" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">See pSEO case study context</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f0ff] to-[#00c8ff] rounded-xl">See pSEO-ready packages</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">Discuss your pSEO scope</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
